products.title: Musa Tigerlily Orange Electric Roller Blind
products.description: Enliven your interior with the musa tigerlily electric roller blind. This blind features a stylised, woodland graphic that really stands out thanks to the warm and vivid orange colour. Simple yet eye-catching, this fabric blind will add a memorable accent colour to any minimalist space, plus the electric design makes it super easy to operate as well as being totally on-trend. Product id: db-erbx2026 fabric colour: tigerlily orange material: 100% polyester headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white steel brackets - top, face or side fix control type: electric control battery powered energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes musa tigerlily orange electric roller blind in orange.
